  <brief_title>Examining an Emergency Room Intervention for the Prevention of Post Traumatic Stress Disorder (PTSD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Interrupting Traumatic Memories: An Emergency Room Intervention for the Prevention of PTSD</official_title>
